node.text: Today is a great day to start to taking steps to create change for Mother Earth. Please join @tentree and I in planting 50,000 trees. I know the words eco friendly or going green can be scary or hopeless but today we can make it easy...if you purchase the “Brie Bella Planting Package” on the tentree site you’ll be making an impactful change by planting trees. Head to my stories to understand how trees do more than being carbon neutral and head to the link in bio to join me on making this planet healthier. ✨

node.text:
I’m a nature girl 👩🏻‍🌾 and it was really important to me to bring that into my children’s lives 🦋 when Birdie was born I was always trying to think of baby activities to get her busy. I quickly realized hiking with her in nature was not only nurturing to her but to me🌲 
Love that I now get to do that with Buddy!!! 
Our @hicolugo carrier is perfect for adventures around the trees, to hear the birds and discover all the sounds of the woods. I love how light weight and comfortable it is for Buddy and I. Extra Bonus is the attached Fanny style pack. Fits my phone, teething treats and more. 🌿 #ColugoPartner

node.text:
A year ago yesterday my Mom went under brain surgery. I’ll never forget the question she was asked if she wanted to wait for surgery so she can make sure to hold her soon to be born grand babies. Everything happened so fast and my mom was so brave and calm through it all. It really showed us how anything can happen at any moment. 
I was so inspired by her courage! She’s a warrior!!! Even though she tells me how challenging it is to look in the mirror everyday, she still has  the desire to help others in her situation. She might not get full movement back in her face but she’ll always have her strength. So proud to call her my Mom!! Love you Mom @kathylaurinaitis 💛✨😘
